Former Top Gear co-host Richard Hammond has released his first home video on YouTube . 
  The 45-year-old is seen shouting 'bored!' to himself and his dog on his farm in Ross-on-Wye . 
  Follows him to Buttermere in the Lake District to learn how to herd sheep . 
  Video has already been watched by 230,000 people and has been called 'Bored 2'